data.description: Walk through now online and view our 3D floor plan of this well maintained patio home! Beautiful engineered hardwood floors in the great room, dining area and kitchen. Open concept that is great for entertaining or relaxing. Bead board in the great room with high ceilings and beautiful molding. Gleaming granite countertops in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances-refrigerator remains, lots of counter space and pantry, the seller just added a gorgeous backsplash. Owner's suite located on the main floor with walk in closet and en suite bath. Half bath on main floor. Upstairs are two nice size bedrooms with walk-in closets plus a large bonus room that could be used as a 4th bedroom. Full bath with double vanity completes the upstairs. Lots of storage with pull down stairs and walk in attic. Faux wood blinds on all windows. Architectural shingles, covered back porch, seller just expended the patio, and privacy fenced back yard. Seller just had the yard leveled and installed new sod. 100% USDA financing available for qualified buyers, Seller offering 5k towards buyers closing costs. Convenient to USC Aiken, Bridgestone, Family Y, shopping and quaint downtown Aiken. Be sure this one is on your list!
